data.description: Come see this 4 bedroom 2 bath home in Palm Heights, minutes from downtown SA on a corner lot. Home comes with central A/C, stainless steel gas stove cooking, stainless steel refrigerator & stainless steel dishwasher all included with sale. Spacious laundry/utility room, walk in shower, walk in closets & much more. Conveniently located to all major highways, shopping, restaurants, etc. Motivated seller, priced below market value, selling as is. Don't miss out on this opportunity, schedule your showing today.
